about.description: A Python implementation of the Frequent Pattern Growth algorithm.
about.summary: A Python implementation of the Frequent Pattern Growth algorithm.

name: pyfpgrowth
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyfpgrowth" %}
{% set version = "1.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "a3e5780385241d90d3ae5cabcca767eb65427b0a908014d42164b3ea8899f1d0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pyfpgrowth

about:
  home: https://github.com/evandempsey/fp-growth
  license: ISC
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A Python implementation of the Frequent Pattern Growth algorithm.'
  description: |
    A Python implementation of the Frequent Pattern Growth algorithm.
  doc_url: https://fp-growth.readthedocs.org
  dev_url: https://github.com/evandempsey/fp-growth

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - CurtLH
